pageContext.description: width mouth 37,5mm; width edge 52.3mm; width loop 7.2mm; breadth mouth 34.5mm; depth socket 96mm,Upper mouth moulding with flattish, near level top; second moulding - small bronze rib; body facets with rather rounded angles; crack in top of one blade tip poss. created in edge sharpening; very narrow socket end; v. little of fine casting flash surviving
pageContext.patina: V. dark brown patina; mostly obscured by granular light-green surfaces
pageContext.surface: Parts of edge blunted a little by modern interference; one tip broken in antiquity; scratches along edge appear to bite gold - poss. recent, as also one or two patches on body. Light orange-brown soil adhering.
